Wayne Morris (American actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayne_Morris_(American_actor) 0 Wayne Morris (February 17, 1914 – September 14, 1959) was an American film and television actor, as well as a decorated World War II fighter ace. He appeared in many films, including Paths of Glory (1957), The Bushwackers (1952), and the title role of Kid Galahad (1937).
